    public interface TElement
extends HasID, THasPropertyChange, java.beans.PropertyChangeListener, java.io.Serializable
    The base for all TEAL componenets. Any object which may be specified, included or defined within the simulation must implement this interface, including physical, graphic, control objects and simulation viewers.

    All TElements are JavaBean complient. As a result many of the attribute processing methods are handled via the JavaBean interfaces and PropertyChange patterns.

    Version:
    $Revision: 1.11 $
    Author:
    Andrew McKinney, Phil Bailey, Michael Danziger
